title: 15 Jash
text: 15 Jash (, meaning "15 Years", before 2004: им.15-летия Октября "im. 15-letiya Oktyabrya") is a village in <a href="Osh%20Region">Osh Region</a> of <a href="Kyrgyzstan">Kyrgyzstan</a>. It is part of the <a href="%C3%96zg%C3%B6n%20District">Özgön District</a>. Its population was 685 in 2021.
